languages.text: "Мне нет дел до беспокойств каких-то культистов. Вели прогнать их туда, откуда они выползли!"
"I do not have time to listen to the concerns of cultists. Tell them to crawl back into whatever hole they came from and never bother me again!"
languages.original_text: "Мне нет дел до беспокойств каких-то культистов. Вели прогнать их туда, откуда они выползли!"

traits.locale_text: "I have no time for the concerns of some cultists. Have them sent back to whatever hole they crawled out of!"

languages.text: « Je n'ai pas le temps de m'occuper des cultistes et de leurs petits problèmes. Dites-leur donc de retourner ramper dans leur trou et de ne plus jamais venir me déranger ! »
languages.original_text: "I do not have time to listen to the concerns of cultists. Tell them to crawl back into whatever hole they came from and never bother me again!"

traits.locale_text: « Je n'ai pas le temps de m'occuper des cultistes et de leurs petits problèmes. Dites-leur donc de retourner ramper dans leur trou et de ne plus jamais venir me déranger ! »

languages.text: «No tengo tiempo para escuchar los problemas de los sectarios. ¡Dígales que vuelvan al agujero del que hayan salido y que no vuelvan a importunarme!».
languages.original_text: "I do not have time to listen to the concerns of cultists. Tell them to crawl back into whatever hole they came from and never bother me again!"

traits.locale_text: «No tengo tiempo para escuchar los problemas de los sectarios. ¡Dígales que vuelvan al agujero del que hayan salido y que no vuelvan a importunarme!».

languages.text: “我没时间听什么乱七八糟的教徒说他们的事情。让他们从哪来就滚回哪去，别再来烦我了！”
languages.original_text: "I do not have time to listen to the concerns of cultists. Tell them to crawl back into whatever hole they came from and never bother me again!"

traits.locale_text: “我没时间听什么乱七八糟的教徒说他们的事情。让他们从哪来就滚回哪去，别再来烦我了！”

languages.text: 「魔女団の不安について聞いている暇はない。あいつらには、這いずり出てきた穴に戻るように言っておいてくれ。もう二度と私の邪魔はするな！」
languages.original_text: "I do not have time to listen to the concerns of cultists. Tell them to crawl back into whatever hole they came from and never bother me again!"

traits.locale_text: 「魔女団の不安について聞いている暇はない。あいつらには、這いずり出てきた穴に戻るように言っておいてくれ。もう二度と私の邪魔はするな！」

languages.text: "Ich habe keine Zeit, mir die Beschwerden von Kultisten anzuhören. Sagt ihnen, sie sollen wieder in das Loch kriechen, aus dem sie gekommen sind, und mich nie wieder belästigen!"
languages.original_text: "I do not have time to listen to the concerns of cultists. Tell them to crawl back into whatever hole they came from and never bother me again!"

languages.text: "Tarikatçıların endişelerini dinleyecek vaktim yok. Onlara çıktıkları deliğe sürünerek geri dönmelerini ve beni bir daha rahatsız etmemelerini söyle!"
